Document: ZIPPacker
Path: godot/classes/class_zippacker.rst
Summary: Provides methods for creating and manipulating ZIP archives.

Inherits: RefCounted < Object

The ZIPPacker class allows you to create and manage ZIP archives programmatically. It offers functionalities to add files, directories, and other archives to a ZIP file, as well as extract contents. This class is useful for tasks such as packaging game assets, distributing data, or handling compressed file storage.
